Face-Emotion-detector/
│
├── images/                # Dataset (downloaded from Kaggle)
│   ├── train/             # Training images (angry, happy, sad, etc.)
│   └── test/              # Testing images
│
├── model/                 # Saved trained CNN models
│
├── notebooks/             # Jupyter notebooks for experiments
│
├── src/                   # Source code
│   ├── data_preprocessing.py  # Image preprocessing & augmentation
│   ├── train_model.py         # Training script for CNN
│   ├── emotion_detector.py    # Real-time webcam detection
│   └── utils.py               # Helper functions
│
├── requirements.txt       # Python dependencies
├── app.py                 # Main entry point for real-time emotion detection
├── README.md              # Project description & documentation
├── CONTRIBUTING.md        # Contribution guidelines
└── LICENSE                # MIT License
